  m_Name: Step2_Crankshaft
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EngineNarrationStep
  stepLabel: CRANKSHAFT
  narrationText: "This is the crankshaft \u2014 and it's the core of the engine.\n\nNotice
    its offset throws \u2014 those are not random. Each one is positioned at a specific
    angle so that the six cylinders fire in a perfectly timed sequence.\n\nAs it
    spins, it converts the up-and-down force of the pistons into continuous rotation.
    That rotation is what ultimately moves the car."
  voiceOver: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c6351f6f1ef8e224d9d1bcb0157e9c50, type: 3}
